{
  "name": "RPlog_Imperial_Clampdown",
  "title": "Lockdown on Corellia",
  "summary": "As the 501st Legion invades Coronet City under General Petra Doom and Major Davyd Levvis, COMPNOR Director Korynn Fleming oversees an ISB clampdown on the corrupt CorSec police force. Fleming meets his agent Solon Halwinder, who reports that CorSec has been bought off by the Maffi crime organization led by Tyy'sun and that Governor Bailey Laran is too weak to stop it, then coordinates the lockdown with Davyd and Petra aboard the 501st's ship, locking down CorSec facilities and arranging interrogations on the orders of Lord Malign. Governor Laran is arrested at the spaceport and brought aboard the shuttle COMPNOR 1 alongside the captured Twi'lek Colonel Twila Virda, who is suffering a bloodworm working through her arm. After Petra accidentally bloodies Virda and departs in a disturbing predatory mood, Fleming secures both prisoners in chains, tears the mind-disruption device from Laran, and cruelly torments Virda by forcing the bloodworm to chew deeper, leaving the Twi'lek screaming in agony as the shuttle prepares to transport them to the Inquisitor for full interrogation.",
